Sword Art Online: Alicization War of Underworld -THE LAST SEASON-
ソードアート・オンライン アリシゼーション War of Underworld -THE LAST SEASON-

The Underworld War enters a new phase.Vecta and Critter lure thousands of American, Chinese and South-Korean players to Underworld so that Vassago can use them to battle the Human Army. The Human Army gets support from friends from ALO but they are massively outnumbered. In reality, the crew of Rath on the Sea Turtle have to face problems of their own.
